OL,6,FMoving the News at One to Salford
OL,7,Fneed not be an issue for viewers.
OL,8,FBreakfast has proved that a national
OL,9,Fnews programme need not be presented
OL,10,Ffrom London.
OL,12,FIt makes little difference whether a
OL,13,Fpolitician is interviewed by someone
OL,14,Fin London or Salford if they are
OL,15,Fsitting in Millbank. Modern
OL,16,Ftechnology means packages can easily
OL,17,Fbe retrieved from the server no
OL,18,Fmatter where the programme is based.
OL,20,FBut how would the extra time be
OL,21,Ffilled?
OL,3,CChanges for BBC Breakfast and BBC
OL,4,CNews at One?
