OL,6,FExtending the two main news
OL,7,Fprogrammes carries attractions. It
OL,8,Fcould be a cost-effective way to
OL,9,Fbuild on success.
OL,11,FBut tinkering with successful
OL,12,Fprogrammes is always risky.
OL,14,FAnd while, as I have said, there is
OL,15,Fno reason why news programmes cannot
OL,16,Fcome from Salford, it could mean
OL,17,Fdifficult choices for some London
OL,18,Fstaff. The process would need careful
OL,19,Fhandling.
OL,3,CChanges for BBC Breakfast and BBC
OL,4,CNews at One?
